  "text": "In this paper, we will employ an overapproximation technique based on gridding and norm-bounding, described in [CITATION_1] , to construct a polytopic system with a norm-bounded additive uncertainty of the form of (17), satisfying (19). For the sake of brevity, we not discuss this overapproximation technique and refer to [Donkers et al., 2011, Procedure III .1] for a detailed description of the construction of all individual matrices in (17).",
